FuncDef: This command creates a mapping from a range of VLANs (appearing in the wlan-gw encapsulated Layer 2 frame) to a retail service ID.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the start VLAN tag of this range. Values-0 to 4095.
Specifies the end VLAN tag of this range. Values-0 to 4095.
Specifies the identifier of the retail service to be used by default of a value in the retail service map of this interface. Values-1 to 2147483650.
